_data.title: Buy
_data.description:
Puhas is a one stop for all your needs for fresh food and nutrition. We offer the best and freshest produce sourced from our farms directly. We promise the best value for your money and reduce the hassle of finding the cleanest nutrition for your family.

Puhas is Jharkhand's growing online supermarket shopping app, trusted by many happy customers and counting! Shop anytime, anywhere from a range of  categories that guarantees all the alphabet letters of Vitamins and including farm-fresh fruits and vegetables, groceries. Enjoy hassle-free online grocery shopping and contactless home delivery at just a click of a button.

_data.name: Puhas
_data.title: Farm Fresh
_data.bio: With a mission of delivering the freshest vegetables and fruits to the retail grocery stores and consumers directly, Puhas is a B2B2C enterprise with a unique approach toward building bottom-up and efficient supply chains in the FFV (Fresh Fruits and Vegetables) sector.
_data.description: Puhas emerged in the underserved eastern and central India as an endeavour to solve the problems that exist in agriculture that are heavily dependent on the gambles of monsoon and money lenders. Technology being the common denominator of development, Puhas deploys a suite of technology products to enhance the supply chain of FFV. With a purpose-driven product design, Puhas has operationalized a high-frequency technology for production and payments.

_data.title: Farms
_data.description: Puhas works with hundreds of farmers supporting them with knowledge, inputs and marketing. Our grassroots business model ensures the freshest and fairest produce is reached to the end customers. Come experience our work and interact with our farmer partners. Schedule a visit now.

_data.title: Partner
_data.description: Puhas is a complete and integrated solution in the farm-to-plate ecosystem where we are actively involved in partnering with HoReCa (Hotels, Restaurants, Catering), Logistics players, transport agencies and traders. If you are engaged in handling fresh produce regularly, grab the opportunity to grow together in the FFV (fresh fruits and vegetables) business.

_data.title: Sell
_data.description: Are you a kirana owner looking to increase your sales basket? Let us help you expand your business into fresh produce. With Puhas, you can also start meeting your customer demand for fruits and vegetables. While we take care of the inventory, you can happily serve your customers' needs.

GirlScript Summer of Code is the three-month-long Open Source program during summers conducted by GirlScript Foundation, started in 2018, to help beginners get started with Open Source Development while encouraging diversity. Throughout the program, participants contribute to different projects under the guidance of experienced mentors.
tasks: Contributed to several projects built with Python and JavaScript.
Collaborated with like-minded students from across India on team projects.
Discussed breakthrough ideas with several open-source pioneers of the country.

_data.role: Open Source Developer - OpenMRS, LibreHealth, RTEMS and CCExtractorOpen
_data.description: Google Code-in (GCI) was an international annual programming competition hosted by Google LLC that allowed pre-university students to complete tasks specified by various partnering open source organizations.
tasks: Contributed to OpenMRS, LibreHealth, RTEMS, JBoss/WildFly, and CCExtractor.
Collaborated with a team of student designers to spearhead a new brand and design system for established Open Source Organizations.
Learned invaluable skills ranging from documentation to research, training, design, outreach, quality assurance, and coding by working closely with my mentors.

_data.description: Dask is a python library that makes it easy to scale the Python libraries that you know and love like NumPy, pandas, and scikit-learn. As part of the Google Summer of Code 2022, I developed a project, Visualizing the Performance Characteristics of Computations, that aimed to enhance the distributed systems' visualizations by improving the task graphs.
tasks: Redeveloped the computational task graph visualisations by enhancing the visuals while being mentored by Genevieve Buckley (Scientist, Monash University) and Martin Durant (Senior Software and Data Engineer, Anaconda).
Expanded the visual output from 11% to 40% without compromising the performance factor.
Optimized the visualisations of existing dask collections to push extra metadata to the task graphs after discussions with partnering organisations such as NVIDIA.

_data.description: "Initiative on the Forest Economy" is an effort to create partnerships between local communities as custodians of forests, industries as the users and government as facilitators of wealth creation.
tasks: Led the end-to-end design, development, and deployment process of the mobile-ﬁrst application suite for the Forest Governance initiative.
Designed a secure and accountable platform to resolve issues related to forest rights.

Spearheaded the creation of an intuitive and lightweight medium for the community to record up-to-date information on the lands (their ownership, usability, resource value, etc.), ultimately helping in the research studies.

Leveraged the applications for a positive impact in over 300 local communities of Odisha, Himachal Pradesh, and Jharkhand by directly beneﬁtting the lives of 400-500 forest dwellers and community members.

_data.description: Joomla is an award-winning Open Source CMS built and maintained by a strong community of volunteers who strive to produce robust, secure, easy to use software. Evaluating the organization's needs and bolstering the communications across the various verticals.
Helping the mentee contribute and become part of the open source community.

_data.description: Precog is a research organisation that studies, analyses, and builds many elements of social networks (for example, social web systems like Twitter and Facebook), including their security and privacy.

_data.description: Temperate is a 0-1 startup that has developed a new proprietary energy-efficient cooling technology based on dew point cooling. _data.name: Amigos App
_data.description: Amigos is a clever Friend Recommendation Application that inventively suggests friends to Users. The User Database is stored in an array of polished AVL (Adelson-Velsky and Landis) Trees. We are not just any other Social Media. Our remarkable CompatiFriend algorithm is using excellent computation to deliver accurate results.

_data.name: Cat Image Classifier
_data.description: A Python Project implementing and training an L-layer Neural Network to classify cats vs non-cat images by using Logistic Regression and storing a cache to pass information from forward to back propagation (82.4% Accuracy).

_data.name: GIF Your Sorrows Away
_data.description: GYSA (GIF your sorrows away) is a browser extension that displays adorable GIFs of cute animals on your screen at random.

_data.name: GoodBoy - A Discord Bot
_data.description: A Discord bot that contextually reacts to the emotions depicted in the messages by using a RoBERTa-based NLP Model, a multi-class emotion analyzer, trained on 58 million tweets that analyses the messages in real time.

_data.name: Number Sign Classifier
_data.description: A Python Project implementing and training a Deep Neural Network in Tensorflow to classify number signs by using Logistic Regression and applying optimization methods such as (Stochastic) Gradient Descent, Momentum, RMSProp, and Adam (99.1% Accuracy).

_data.name: Paradise Hotel Manager
_data.description: A C++ Project implementing critical functions (add, search, sort, modify, display, delete, payment, check-in & check-out) that are required in a resort/hotel by using an optimised database of rooms and guests.

_data.name: State Library Manager
_data.description: A C++ Project implementing critical functions (add, search, modify, display, delete, payment, issue & return) that are required in a library by using an optimised database of books and customers.

_data.name: Pikachu Objectifier
_data.description: Pikachu Objectifier is a Deep Learning Classifier trained using YOLO (You Only Live Once) and the OpenCV framework for the fine-tuning of the dataset model. I shamelessly objectifiy Pikachus in this project.

_data.name: Terrain Mapper and Rover Maneuver
_data.description: A cross-platform Unity AR mobile application that maps terrain in real time using a camera utility. It also hosts a real time free movement AR Rover which can be maneuvered by touch. Deep applications - Mars Rovers can be simulated using the 3D mapped terrains.
